    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chilli-garlic-and-king-prawn-spaghetti/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>pasta </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the pasta for 7-9 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the<strong> cooked pasta</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chilli-garlic-and-king-prawn-spaghetti/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chilli-garlic-and-king-prawn-spaghetti/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, drain your<strong> king prawns</strong>, then add them to the pan with the <strong>halved cherry tomatoes </strong>and cook for 3 min</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chilli-garlic-and-king-prawn-spaghetti/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>tomato paste</strong> and <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong> and cook for 30 secs further</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chilli-garlic-and-king-prawn-spaghetti/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong> with a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until the prawns are cooked through</p><p>Note: Please make sure you cook your prawns thoroughly (until piping hot!) as cooking equipment varies</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chilli-garlic-and-king-prawn-spaghetti/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained pasta </strong>to the pan with a splash of the<strong> starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Cook for 1 min further, stirring until the sauce thickens \u2013 this is your <strong>chilli, garlic & king prawn pasta</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chilli-garlic-and-king-prawn-spaghetti/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chilli, garlic & king prawn pasta</strong></p><p>Top with a handful of <strong>salad</strong>, a drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>and a grind of<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
